welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Parkes, a charming city known for its beautiful countryside, rich history, and warm community. We invite you to explore all it has to offer and enjoy your stay here."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Parkes Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Parkes Airport handles all freight and cargo operations.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
